docs.snippet: The Obamas have gained and lost in their four years in the White House, becoming seasoned professionals instead of newcomers, yet many close to them see the tolls their roles have taken....
docs.lead_paragraph: The Obamas have gained and lost in their four years in the White House, becoming seasoned professionals instead of newcomers, yet many close to them see the tolls their roles have taken.
docs.abstract: People close to Pres Obama and first lady Michelle say they can see tolls their roles have taken during first term in office; Obamas have gained and lost in their first four years in White House, becoming seasoned professionals instead of newcomers, with contracted sense of possibility.

headline.seo: After 4 Years, Friends See Shifts in Obamas
